<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_304376'><a id="like_count_community_question_304376" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/304376?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">7 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F6218281-the-sweetness-at-the-bottom-of-the-pie">like</a></span>

