  <span id="freeText12968947987071038154" style="display:none"><br />A surprisingly, delightfull who dunnit, introducing Flavia De Luce, who is one of the most captivating, young characters I have met since young Harry came out from his cupboard under the stairs. I'll definitely be reading the next chemical caper.<br /><br /></span>
